name: commit
description: Commits all changes on the current branch with a conventional commit message, then ensures a GitHub PR exists. Use this skill whenever the user says "commit", "commit and push", "ship it", "send a PR", "create a pull request", or any variation of committing and/or opening a PR for their current work. Also triggers on "/commit".
argument-hint: "[optional: description of the changes]"
